  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The first aim of the study is to obtain from chirurgical micro biopsy myoblast in culture
      which will differentiate in Diaphragm fiber. Then these fibers will be submitted under
      mechanical stress condition similar to those imposed in vivo by mechanical ventilation to
      validate in human a model in vitro of diaphragm dysfunction induced by mechanical
      ventilation. Then the second part of the study will be to evaluate with this model, the
      efficiency of an antioxidant therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
